Finesse Slayer		KEY:Slayer Talent ~ Finesse Slayer		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SlayerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.SlayerTalent			VISIBLE:DISPLAY																														DESC:You gain Weapon Finesse as a bonus feat.																																																																																																																												VFEAT:Weapon Finesse																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.53
Firearm Training		KEY:Slayer Talent ~ Firearm Training	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.SlayerTalent																																							DESC:A slayer with this talent gains Exotic Weapon Proficiency (firearms).																																																																																																															AUTO:FEAT|Exotic Weapon Proficiency (Firearms)																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.53
Foil Scrutiny		KEY:Slayer Talent ~ Foil Scrutiny		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SlayerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.SlayerTalent																																			DESC:A slayer with this talent is able to obscure his thoughts and intentions. He gains a +2 bonus on all Bluff and Disguise checks, as well as on Will saving throws to resist mind-reading spells and effects (such as detect thoughts and discern lies).																																																																																																																																	BONUS:SKILL|Bluff,Disguise|2																					SOURCEPAGE:p.53	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+2 Will vs. mind-reading spells and effects
